public void stopcar()
{
sendMessage(“You bring the car to a screeching stop!”);
playerSER = 0x338;
playerSEA = 0x326;
playerSE = 0x328;
playerSEW = 0x333;
playerEnergy = 100;
isRunning2 = false;
sendFrame126(playerEnergy +"%", 149);

updateRequired = true;
}
